     4	/**
     5	 * @internal
     6	 * Sets an account in the vm state manager. Used to set predeploys
     7	 * Has significantly less validation than the setAccountHandler action
     8	 * We don't reuse setAccountAction because of circular dependencies
     9	 * All actions depend on this package.
    10	 * @param {object} params
    11	 * @param {import('@tevm/vm').Vm} params.vm
    12	 * @param {bigint} [params.nonce]
